url: 'https://github.com/vnageshwaran-de/tera-agentic-rag'
abstract: >-
  Companion artifacts for an IEEE Access survey article on
  trustworthy agentic Retrieval-Augmented Generation in
  enterprise settings. The repository releases the
  systematic-review protocol, search strings, screening log,
  bibliography, and the reusable artifacts of the TERA
  framework: an eight-dimension taxonomy, a threat-to-control
  matrix, an agentic-RAG evaluation matrix, a cloud-native
  reference architecture component model, a governance and
  human-oversight checklist, an enterprise lifecycle model,
  and a research roadmap.
keywords:
  - agentic AI
  - artificial intelligence governance
  - cloud computing
  - enterprise AI
  - large language model agents
  - LLMOps
  - MLOps
  - prompt injection
  - retrieval-augmented generation
  - trustworthy AI
